# Claude Sync Notes

## Agent layout (2026-03)

- **`.agents/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`** — workflow agents: `orchestrate`, `coder`, `code-review` (full prompts per Cursor; invoke `/orchestrate`, `/coder`, `/code-review`).
- **`.cursor/skills/`** — `feature-workflow`, `debugger-specialist`, `utility-specialist`.
- **Git:** coder may **commit + push `feature/*`**; **merge to `development`** only after **explicit user approval** (utility / feature-workflow / `gh`, not silent).
- **`.cursor/rules/*.mdc`** — shared constraints; each workflow `SKILL.md` says which rules apply.
- **OpenSpec** — **`/opsx:archive`** only in **`/orchestrate`** **after** **`/code-review`** **READY** (not in coder/review).

